    "description": "Aisan Technology Co.,Ltd. designs, develops, distributes, and maintains CAD systems for the public survey, registration surveying, civil engineering, and construction industries in Japan. The company offers surveying system solutions comprising WingNeoINFINITY; ATM'S Home; e-collector; and LASPORT, a land system port; and AreaScan. It also provides MMS/point cloud services, which includes WingEarth, a point cloud processing tool, mobile mapping system, MMS post-processing solution, and point cloud encyclopedia. In addition, the company offers mobility solutions including high precision 3D map data and position solutions, 3D data processing software, autonomous driving system development and smart city solution, and other solutions, such as drone surveying solution, and HandzReco, a character recognition engine. Aisan Technology Co.,Ltd. was incorporated in 1970 and is headquartered in Nagoya, Japan."
